一直相信孟女士是清白的。我们也一直相信加拿大的司法体系。华为一直支持孟女士寻求正义和自由，今天我们依旧坚持这一立场。」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-e0b51b668852a1a6df4f23ac1ecf8b56_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "83 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/480855599"}}, "attached_info": "ClQI1/XSiJ7mwed4EAMaCDY5MTM4NDMyIOv+9ogGMAc4aEAjcgk0ODA4NTU1OTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "36_1629352964.0983758", "card_id": "Q_479952143", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "游戏《明日方舟》最成功的活动是哪一次？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c2da19fdc27582290a824c18bd108762_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/479952143"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I1/XSiJ7mwed4EAMaCDY4OTM3NDI2INyT5IgGMAA4JUAkcgk0Nzk5NTIxNDN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1629352964.0989735", "card_id": "Q_480640639", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "莆田交警通报蔚来自动驾驶事件「已开展调查，将依法责任认定」，事件还有哪些值得关注的信息？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a47ec66174b722686259a5cc2a6db23d_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "80 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/480640639"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I1/XSiJ7mwed4EAMaCDY5MDkwMzgxIMy78ogGMAE4VkAlcgk0ODA2NDA2Mzl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1629352964.0998955", "card_id": "Q_472588446", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "打官司，负责